name: Baking Queen
description:
She bakes amazing breads in her stone oven. The smell surrounds this cute village. So cute that you can see tourists in streets taking pictures, tasting the traditional local wine of the village. People tastes dozens of different flavored wines, indecisive ones gets tipsy with all that and thats when the bread smell gets you and walk you through the streets until you see her friendly smile. If you decide to tell her that she is pretty like I did, she’d say “Im too old to be pretty i was pretty 20 years ago not now” And then she will look down. 

April 2017 From one of our travel to Şirince. 

Im trying to remind myself how magical the travelling , how inspiring it is. I hope you enjoy the little story.
